@startuml Sequence Diagram - AI Chat Interaction
!theme cerulean-outline

title SmartMedia - AI Chatbot Interaction Sequence

actor User
participant "AIChatbot\nComponent" as Chatbot
participant "AppStore" as Store
participant "Electron\nIPC" as IPC
participant "Python\nEngine" as Python
participant "Qwen2-VL\nModel" as Model
participant "SQLite\nDatabase" as DB

User -> Chatbot: Click AI Chatbot FAB
activate Chatbot

Chatbot -> Chatbot: setState({ isOpen: true })
Chatbot -> User: Show chat interface

== User Query - Text Search ==

User -> Chatbot: Type: "Show me photos\nfrom the beach"
activate User

Chatbot -> Chatbot: Update input state

User -> Chatbot: Click Send
Chatbot -> Chatbot: Add user message\nto messages[]

Chatbot -> Chatbot: setIsLoading(true)

Chatbot -> Store: Get all images
activate Store
Store -> Chatbot: images[]
deactivate Store

Chatbot -> Chatbot: Filter images by:\n• tags: "beach"\n• objects: "ocean", "sand"\n• scene: "outdoor"

Chatbot -> Chatbot: Format response:\n"Found 15 beach photos"

Chatbot -> Chatbot: Add AI response\nto messages[]

Chatbot -> Chatbot: setIsLoading(false)
Chatbot -> User: Display results\nwith image grid

deactivate User

== User Query - Image Analysis ==

User -> Chatbot: Click "Attach Image"
activate User

Chatbot -> User: Show image picker
User -> Chatbot: Select image

Chatbot -> Chatbot: Set selectedImage\nLoad preview

User -> Chatbot: Type: "What's in\nthis photo?"

Chatbot -> Chatbot: Add message with\nimage attachment

Chatbot -> IPC: aiChat(imagePath,\n"What's in this photo?")
activate IPC

IPC -> Python: {"action": "ai_chat",\n"image_path": path,\n"message": query}
activate Python

Python -> Model: Load image\nPrepare vision input
activate Model

Model -> Model: Vision-language\nprocessing

Model -> Python: Generated response:\n"This photo shows a golden\nretriever playing in a park\nwith a frisbee."
deactivate Model

Python -> IPC: {"success": true,\n"response": text}
deactivate Python

IPC -> Chatbot: Chat response
deactivate IPC

Chatbot -> Chatbot: Add AI response\nto messages[]

Chatbot -> User: Display AI answer\nwith image preview

deactivate User

== User Query - Metadata Request ==

User -> Chatbot: Type: "When was\nthis taken?"
activate User

Chatbot -> Store: getImage(selectedImageId)
activate Store
Store -> Chatbot: ImageMetadata
deactivate Store

Chatbot -> Chatbot: Extract dateScanned:\n"2024-06-15"

Chatbot -> Chatbot: Format response:\n"This photo was scanned\non June 15, 2024"

Chatbot -> User: Display metadata

deactivate User

== User Query - Complex Search ==

User -> Chatbot: Type: "Find photos of\npeople smiling at\nevents"
activate User

Chatbot -> Store: Get all images
activate Store
Store -> Chatbot: images[]
deactivate Store

Chatbot -> Chatbot: Filter by:\n• face_count > 0\n• emotion: "happy"\n• album_category: "Events"

Chatbot -> DB: Query images with\nfilters
activate DB

DB -> DB: SELECT * FROM images\nWHERE metadata->>'album_category' = 'Events'\nAND metadata->>'emotion' = 'happy'

DB -> Chatbot: Matching images
deactivate DB

Chatbot -> Chatbot: Format results:\n"Found 23 happy moments\nfrom events"

Chatbot -> User: Display grid of\nmatching images

deactivate User

== User Action - Navigate to Image ==

User -> Chatbot: Click image in\nchat results
activate User

Chatbot -> Chatbot: Find image index\nin filtered list

Chatbot -> Chatbot: Open PhotoViewer\nwith image

Chatbot -> User: Show full-screen\nimage viewer

deactivate User

== User Action - Clear Chat ==

User -> Chatbot: Click menu →\n"Clear History"
activate User

Chatbot -> Chatbot: setMessages([])

Chatbot -> User: Show empty chat\nwith suggestions

User -> Chatbot: Click "X" to close
Chatbot -> Chatbot: setState({ isOpen: false })
Chatbot -> User: Hide chat interface

deactivate User
deactivate Chatbot

note over User, Chatbot
  **Quick Actions**
  • "Show me favorites"
  • "Photos from last week"
  • "Find documents"
  • "Selfies only"
  • "Pictures with [name]"
end note

note over Python, Model
  **AI Chat Capabilities**
  • Image description
  • Object identification
  • Scene explanation
  • Activity recognition
  • Emotion interpretation
  • Contextual Q&A
end note

note over Chatbot, DB
  **Search Features**
  • Natural language queries
  • Date range filtering
  • Tag-based search
  • Face-based search
  • Emotion filtering
  • Album filtering
end note

@enduml
